<title>CALVARI</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa Kalvari-ah thi,
 Ziechun ka Lal a khenden ui;
 Kross-ah kei di'n A thisan luong,
 Ka ngaihdamna ziechun A chawi.

[V2]
 Aw Kalvari, Kalvari thim,
 Kei di'n Isu thisan luonna;
 Aw Kalvari, Kalvari pha,
 Hukdampa thii, ziechun kei di'n.

[V3]
 2. Suongpi khi leh van nim lakah,
 Ka Hukdampa khunin, A thii;
 Puonzak kithek chun a hihlang,
 Van kipahna leh ni tawplo.

[V4]
 3. Aw Lal Isu, bangtin ahim,
 Kei dinga Na hinna nei piek?
 Kross pu ding leh lunggim dingin,
 Phat lauh umah Kalvari ah.</lyrics>
</song>